data.description: Discover contemporary living in this ranch home nestled in the Riverbrooke community. LVP flows throughout the open kitchen and living area, creating a seamless space for relaxation and entertaining. The spacious kitchen features sleek appliances and a breakfast bar, perfect for casual dining or hosting gatherings. Retreat to the primary suite with its luxurious tub and shower, offering a serene escape after a long day. Convenience is key with a mudroom off the garage, complete with a laundry combination. Outside, a covered back patio and a fenced-in backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Located near shopping, dining and close proximty to Fort Liberty his home offers the ideal blend of tranquility and accessibility.
